reviews.review_text: My First Show Thank Yoy Good Buddy...Hi Rob S.

All You Can Eat Pizza Funny the different things we all remember from shows, mostly great shows.  I loved this show, although the venue was really hot...oh, wait a second - I thought I was reviewing Kile Aud in KS in August 82... sorry!  this show was great too!  Love the Dupree Diamond Blues...the Dead always seemed to like CCCC and Portland with its quirky roller-rink sound - just check the shows year after year in the early 80's...but there were few 'bad' shows in that time frame, huh?...what concert don't you love that has a Morning Dew in it?  After my first Dead Concert in Portland I hitched home to take a French test in junior year of HS.. after this show, i think I poked my gf for 24 hours straight...until the show at Boston Garden...
